snippet.title: Final Rush Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for Final Rush, the new First Person Shooter made by Strike Games.

Final Rush is now on sale on steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/263480/?featured_app=1

 For more information, http://www.strikegames.net/finalrush.html
